{"tid":2443630,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【新手爸爸】擁餅印女合照慈父樣盡現　呂方囡囡Emma雙眼似足爸爸","createTime":"2021-03-12T07:26:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-12T09:35:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bac9383dbf5251db454361e8e24bd16ff48eafc8","tid":2443630,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:26:52.000Z","msg":"現年57歲的呂方，在去年5月與年齡相差16載的圈外女友伍惠寶（Rainbow）結婚。在8月初，太太伍惠寶誕下女兒呂晨，呂方「升呢」為人父。<br />\n<br />\n不經不覺，呂方囡囡已經7個月大，一副有女萬事足的他不時於社交平台分享女兒的照片。昨日（3月11日），他在個人Facebook分享一張抱著女兒的照片，從相中可見他展現慈父模樣外，也可見小千金跟呂方如餅印一樣。<br />\n<br />\n女兒與呂方如餅印<br />\n呂方昨日於個人facebook分享兩張跟女兒呂辰（Emma）合照，只見這位新手爸爸把女兒緊緊地抱住，當中他留言：「我的寶貝！」女兒果然是爸爸的前世情人。<br />\n<br />\n從照片所見，7個月大的Emma皮膚白哲面仔圓圓，雙眼似足爸爸，十足倒模了爸爸呂方一樣，而網民也大讚Emma可愛，有人更留言說：「BB超得意又似吕方，好可愛啊！」<br />\n<br />\n呂方於去年5月與有「網絡買餸天后」之稱，擁半億身家的伍惠寶（Rainbow）結婚，二人雙喜臨門，女兒於8月初出世。雖然呂方與Rainbow年齡相距16載，不過二人同樣對健康食療有興趣，加上喜愛運動如踩單車等。<br />\n<br />\n另外呂方可說是愛妻號，原本居於元朗獨立屋的他，婚後為了讓太太及女兒住得舒適，故婚後搬往同屋苑一間較大的獨立屋。<br />\n<br />\n從呂方夫婦於社交平台分享的照片所見，獨立屋樓高三層連天台，坐擁開揚的景觀，另外屋內環境十分闊落，二人更飼養了兩頭愛犬。而榮升父親的呂方近日喜歡留在家陪伴妻女，閒時會跟太太出外踩單車，生活寫意。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2895000/2899564/LuiFong_thumb_20210312_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2895000%2F2899564%2FLuiFong_thumb_20210312_ch_1024.jpg&h=51b9a8ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2895000/2899564/158791525_1871030063061522_619965448565567163_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2895000%2F2899564%2F158791525_1871030063061522_619965448565567163_n_1024.jpg&h=f2429f47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2895000/2899564/159093135_1871030086394853_8885470667629940747_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2895000%2F2899564%2F159093135_1871030086394853_8885470667629940747_n_1024.jpg&h=383e2abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static02-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2895000/2899564/154348787_444298279955896_1006561876404507513_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic02-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2895000%2F2899564%2F154348787_444298279955896_1006561876404507513_n_1024.jpg&h=561a2041&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"86f6a082921cfa75321d4d0f30ec0fb0248aaf11","tid":2443630,"uid":232748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:28:08.000Z","msg":"dodo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b077db0f25bd0b138630b8ca2ef8c2f03d46bff","tid":2443630,"uid":93986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:33:55.000Z","msg":"條女41歲仲生到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f9e789377bb3f8807a9ae78155ff2a03d30bc9","tid":2443630,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:34:56.000Z","msg":"男方"},{"pid":"9d20a6890ff08b85e93fe543744776c2e736abe6","tid":2443630,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:36:03.000Z","msg":"條女中學畢業老豆已經⋯"},{"pid":"36fb0c2c145aaea51d42c45ded5fc9b2ee37967c","tid":2443630,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d20a6890ff08b85e93fe543744776c2e736abe6","tid":2443630,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:36:03.000Z","msg":"條女中學畢業老豆已經⋯"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:38:03.000Z","msg":"唔好講到咁遠，淨係小學畢業果陣，個老豆已經差唔多七張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1d6762ce72816c94a4e4ed0fab6aeb4750189d","tid":2443630,"uid":323720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-12T07:38:06.000Z"